'''2015年10月亚丁导弹袭击'''，发生于2015年10月6日。一群袭击者将导弹瞄准[[也门总理|也门]]副总统兼[[也门总理|总理]]所在的Al-Qasr酒店。酒店同时也是支持总统[[阿卜杜拉布·曼苏尔·哈迪|哈迪]]的也门军队的军事基地。也门运输部长巴德尔·巴萨尔马怀疑[[胡塞武装|胡塞武装]]是此次袭击的幕后黑手，但[[伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯兰国]]声称对袭击负责。<ref name="alarabiya">{{Cite web|title=ISIS claims deadly Aden attacks on Arab troops|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/10/06/Yemen-s-VP-hotel-residence-attacked.html|accessdate=2015-10-12|date=2015-10-06|work=Al Arabiya News English|archive-date=2019-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909171940/http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/10/06/Yemen-s-VP-hotel-residence-attacked.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Islamic State kills 22 in attacks on Yemen government, Gulf troops, mosque|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-aden-hotel-idUSKCN0S009E20151006|accessdate=6 March 2016|author=Mohammed Mukhashaf|date=6 October 2015|work=Reuters|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810214523/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-yemen-security-aden-hotel-idUSKCN0S009E20151006|dead-url=no}}</ref>

